name: Thai Communicable Diseases Act B.E. 2558 Explorer
description: An interactive web application to read, search, and reference the Thai Communicable Diseases Act B.E. 2558 (พระราชบัญญัติโรคติดต่อ พ.ศ. ๒๕๕๘). Designed for legal professionals, public health officials, and the general public for easy navigation and understanding of the law.
